{"tid":720723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【消防苦勸3小時】女子危站樓頂 圍觀者用強光燈阻救援","createTime":"2018-06-28T06:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T16:55:13.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4446441a0f425490504963dc0456aada8f3d75","tid":720723,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:52:18.000Z","msg":"今日內地媒體報道，6月26日晚，江蘇南通一名女子爬到大廈樓頂想要輕生，當地消防部門緊急趕到現場。但是在救援過程中，樓下圍觀者卻用燈照刺激並起哄「跳啊，跳啊」，消防中隊副中隊長立即喝止了他們。<br />\n<br />\n為避免刺激女子，消防隊員趴在平台上小心觀察，其他隊員則和民警一起苦苦勸說。沒想到還有人爬到更高的樓層，依舊嘗試用強光燈去照女子所在的頂樓，阻礙救援，經過消防和公安3個多小時的工作，最終女子放棄了輕生念頭。<br />\n<br />\n中國消防向大眾呼籲：「別擾亂消防員救援行動，請對生命多些敬畏！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180628/58372666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180628%2F58372666&d=F9d%2FgIgD8apEe27ZTW%2FZcKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f6c331a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180628%2F58372666&h=0833f00e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180628/58372666</a>"},{"pid":"da026c7f5d6e08f38a312bfddbcb7d32b390179e","tid":720723,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b91aaa87dfa2c355beb66d722ec6b08670666bb","tid":720723,"uid":4166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:58:57.000Z","msg":"你不跳，爺的抖音拍不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04aba4fbeb7e8a48c53c411ad4457f413c61182b","tid":720723,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"呃like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4438685c03b7eb7c860172fd5f2e76749a7e8034","tid":720723,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:35:01.000Z","msg":"做乜唔跳？ 順便整死幾隻支那畜生。你唔跳都求其搵d野掟死樓下班畜生啦"},{"pid":"2b13f256ce510c8949facee0f401ce593cbcb64b","tid":720723,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:43:11.000Z","msg":"好中國"},{"pid":"8a2dca3c22a679cf57af42d4a5f930b103bdc7b5","tid":720723,"uid":66527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">成件事</span>好中國</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2d281e9de0cebc8d3202c585a9932fe09cf59d3a","tid":720723,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"原來大陸都好人<br />\n<br />\n我指叫佢跳個班人"},{"pid":"5701776842f7a39d6b4814e2ad8e5603d2feb370","tid":720723,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:55:13.000Z","msg":"支那咁多直播，又抖音<br />\n<br />\n實成班花生友拍片睇人跳樓"}]}